00:02:08.500 --> 00:02:10.533
What about you? Do you believe in mermaids?

00:02:10.533 --> 00:02:11.560
I do.

00:02:11.560 --> 00:02:12.780
And I also believe...

00:02:12.780 --> 00:02:15.280
that merfolk
and humans can never coexist.

00:02:15.280 --> 00:02:16.470
Have a drink with me.

00:02:16.470 --> 00:02:17.960
But I'm still on the clock.

00:02:17.960 --> 00:02:21.960
If a customer asks you to drink, you drink.

00:02:21.960 --> 00:02:23.890
You didn't tell me you were coming.

00:02:23.890 --> 00:02:26.030
I was trying to surprise you.

00:02:26.030 --> 00:02:28.650
And I ended up getting a surprise of my own.

00:02:28.650 --> 00:02:32.000
The real reason I came was to talk to you
in person about our relationship.

00:02:32.000 --> 00:02:34.290
- I think--
- Let's break up.

00:02:34.290 --> 00:02:36.320
I saw the design you were sketching.

00:02:36.320 --> 00:02:38.120
So I had it custom-made for you.

00:02:38.120 --> 00:02:40.000
Nava, let me put it on for you.

00:02:41.110 --> 00:02:42.840
Where were you?

00:02:42.840 --> 00:02:43.920
Where I go is my--

00:02:43.920 --> 00:02:46.140
I followed the car you and Phraphai were in.

00:02:46.140 --> 00:02:47.580
What did you say?

00:02:47.580 --> 00:02:50.120
That's Phraphai's car.

00:02:50.120 --> 00:02:51.730
Do you realize

00:02:51.730 --> 00:02:53.620
that what you just did

00:02:53.620 --> 00:02:56.150
is a complete invasion of my privacy?

00:02:56.150 --> 00:02:57.900
Can't you just tell me?

00:02:57.900 --> 00:03:00.455
Just tell me you feel something for me, too.

00:03:35.644 --> 00:03:37.055
Oh, Phurich.

00:03:37.055 --> 00:03:38.900
You're awake.

00:03:45.533 --> 00:03:48.700
I made you some hot porridge.
It'll help your hangover.

00:03:48.700 --> 00:03:50.400
If you're not hungry yet,

00:03:50.400 --> 00:03:52.611
I'll grab you some clothes to change into.

00:03:52.611 --> 00:03:53.730
It's okay.

00:03:53.730 --> 00:03:56.688
I think I might've left some in the car.

00:04:05.450 --> 00:04:07.922
Is there something on my face?

00:04:12.320 --> 00:04:14.955
I was just thinking about last night.

00:04:25.730 --> 00:04:28.466
I'll go grab you some clothes to change into.

